  "title": "Allure",
  "description": "The Vanilla feel of Minecraft but... cuter!",
  "body": "<center>\n<h1 id=\"-allure-https-cdn-modrinth-com-data-cached_images-25a4c46694c80f132aca77eb734555b1c517a8e8-png-\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/4d5e345af75b41c960f7052fac891045b8286834.png\" alt=\"Allure\"></h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/allure-pack/\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8a2dd1324a19f7594a6e032659b78fb3e5e89a2d.png\" alt=\"Modrinth\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/texture-pack/allure-6439754/\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/48f3ed3f11e619ef7fea93c4344ae8f4ba233cb0.png\" alt=\"Planet Minecraft\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/p4ncake\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/1fab8f2e1518ab9f6373586085d9aa785e0e3b9d.png\" alt=\"Support me on Ko-Fi\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/C9Q6XFG8T8\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/6f5a8b8552da877af71a331499e3fffcb57b513a.png\" alt=\"Join our Community on Discord!\"></a></p><hr><p><strong>Allure</strong> is a 16x16 W.I.P Resourcepack which with its vibrant palette and its shading style makes Minecraft cuter in a way. One of the main goals for the pack (besides containing every single texture there is in Minecraft) is wide compatibility, the pack will have ports ranging even from Minecraft Alpha 1.2.2 (the first Minecraft version in which Texturepacks were introduced). <hr></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/Al41w13V/images/f8d27dac82f7755f504b3f05464a5327db6de6eb.png\" alt=\"Minecraft\">\n(Build and Posing made by <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/Quoraal\">Quoraal</a>)<hr><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/Al41w13V/images/a51613dc39e9b4c09dc2007373bcacd08d424688.webp\" alt=\"Enchanting table room\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/Al41w13V/images/a60f5f8993280bdad0bb114b5bae067bde35227d.webp\" alt=\"A cute base in a birch forest\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/Al41w13V/images/564f3d0935190f0b10fe64197eedaab60cff65e6.webp\" alt=\"End portal\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/allure-pack/gallery\"><img alt=\"More Images\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/3d2a1b4086461ba3aa4dd2c0a8afe2e9aa1e252b_0.webp\"></a></p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Frequently Asked Questions:</h2>\n<details>\n<summary>Does <b>Allure</b> require any Mods to work?</summary>\nNo, you don't need any mods to play with Allure. If you're gonna play with mods though, please don't use Optifine, Allure makes use of the vanilla core shaders functionality which is not usually compatible with Optifine. If you're playing on Fabric though, it is recommended to play with Sodium, ETF, EMF, Continuity and Polytone.\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>What Mods does <b>Allure</b> Support?</summary>\nAllure's main goal is to be universally compatible with everything, so here is a list of compatible mods to use with the pack:\n</br></br></br>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/appleskin\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/bf2ace9afb60993e84fa57ce1233169fda76147e.png\" alt=\"AppleSkin\" width=\"45%\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/eating-animation\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/ddcf28ce4287352bbd5cc3ade61cc1ebb02eb013.png\" alt=\"Eating Animation\" width=\"45%\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/axiom\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/bdd5eedb2f817a264ada2313a7f5018ff24d4e7f.png\" alt=\"Axiom\" width=\"45%\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/make_bubbles_pop\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/6850c1ab03252f61a829eca65ef306b7745c5849.png\" alt=\"Make Bubbles Pop\" width=\"45%\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/armor-toughness-bar\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/65fbf35fbb604934ff9eaf522b0eee95fc6e964c.png\" alt=\"Armor Toughness Bar\" width=\"45%\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/crafting-tweaks\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/47ff8e93c59f8f87809eb71792412104eed9be3b_0.webp\" alt=\"Crafting Tweaks\" width=\"45%\"></a>\n\n</details>\n<hr>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/e7887614b1e17bec66022c5f2ba62343088d36d3.png\" alt=\"Allure is still W.I.P, if you find any bugs or want to give feedback, consider joining my Discord server!\"></p>\n<p>The pack is still in the works so please be patient for updates 💛\nIf you want to get notified for updates on the pack progress, consider joining my Discord server <a href=\"https://discord.gg/C9Q6XFG8T8\">here</a>!</p>\n<br><br><hr>\n<h1>Other Projects!</h1>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/allure-fresh-animations-support\"><img alt=\"Allure Fresh Animations Support\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a4b12553ad59462994b06b9f7124fd36c9a81138.webp\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/allure-emoji-pack\"><img alt=\"Allure Emoji Pack\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/62de9de72ccd55e8a14fd4b637eb9c54dd0fb888.png\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/allure-3d-plants\"><img alt=\"Allure 3D Plants\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a46651adb88e91abf37823d73fa1b42f66d4b596.webp\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/allure-dark-theme-gui\"><img alt=\"Allure Dark Theme GUI\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/f8deee765f891b6ca092c2ae5c120c8ea01c9007.webp\"></a>\n</center>",
